title: dabloon
author: dabloon
content: Hi I made a meme coin token based on the dabloon tiktok meme if you want to join our discord I will send you some for free https://discord.gg/9aXD2sYB.There is not need to purchase, you can earn dabloons for posting art commenting etc i add a couple bucks on pancakeswap so people can trade it for BNB tooThe token has a max supply of 2 BillionThe thing is, the dabloon meme is funny, but because it's an imaginary currency on tiktok, there's not much to do, so I thought we turn it into a real cryptocurrency and people can start tipping people for fun or go to the markets to buy art.I don't expect this token to have value, it's just a fun experiment.You can also see our website (it is under construction so if you have any new idea for it let me know) https://cryptodabloons.com/
